                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-826" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE PURDEN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a shoemaker, living in Stafford-street, Lisson-grove. When I went home, on the 19th of May, I found my window broken, and two pairs of shoes gone—these are them.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184206130156"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420613-name-827" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-827" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
